		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:新細明體,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0b1e1f&quot;&gt;五、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:STKaiti&quot;&gt;The operation of the company&amp;#39;s establishment of nomination or other various functional committees&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;EB Garamond&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0b1e1f&quot;&gt;In accordance with the regulations, the company set up a remuneration committee on December 27, 2011 by the board of directors&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

			&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;EB Garamond&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0b1e1f&quot;&gt;Comply with the requirements of the regulation of Practice on Governance of Listed Companies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;width:220.25pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;width:652.55pt&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:新細明體,serif&quot;&gt;六、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:STKaiti&quot;&gt;If the company has established a practice on corporate governance in accordance with the &amp;quot;Principle of practice on Corporate Governance of Listed Companies&amp;quot;, please describe the differences between its operation and the practice on corporate governance as stipulated:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;width:652.55pt&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:STKaiti&quot;&gt;The company has not formulated principle for corporate governance, but practically, in addition to the spirit of the practice for corporate governance of listed companies and the implementation of corporate governance by measuring the scale of the company&amp;rsquo;s organization, business operations have complied with the company law and securities-related laws and regulations, and should cover the main governance in principle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;width:652.55pt&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:新細明體,serif&quot;&gt;七、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:STKaiti&quot;&gt;Other important information that helps to understand the operation of corporate governance (such as employee rights, employee care, investor relations, supplier relations, rights of stakeholders, training of directors and supervisors, risk management policies and risk measurement standards) Execution, execution of customer policies, company purchasing liability insurance for directors and supervisors, etc.):&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;width:652.55pt&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:STKaiti&quot;&gt;1.The company put great emphasis e on employee relations. In addition to setting up an employee welfare committee and providing marriage and funeral subsidies, it also organizes employee spring party etc. In order to ensure the rights and interests of employees, it has formulated personnel management regulations in accordance with the Labor Standards Act, and provided employees with work rules to follow. There are employee reward and punishment management regulations and various welfare systems, so that employees can follow the code of conduct and workplace ethics to ensure legitimate rights and interests; encourage employees to communicate with management, appropriately reflect employees&amp;#39; opinions, improve labor-management communication and management, and protect labor rights and interests.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;width:652.55pt&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;EB Garamond&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0b1e1f&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:STKaiti&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Situation of training for directors and supervisors: The directors and supervisors of the company are required by laws and regulations to plan relevant professional knowledge and practical operation courses for directors and supervisors to continue their education.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;width:652.55pt&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;EB Garamond&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0b1e1f&quot;&gt;3.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:STKaiti&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Implementation of risk management policies and risk measurement standards: The company focuses on its own business. In addition to cooperating with laws and regulations to implement various policies, it also conducts risk assessments for major customers and suppliers to reduce and avoid possible risks.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;width:652.55pt&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:STKaiti&quot;&gt;4.The situation where the company purchases liability insurance for directors and supervisors: The directors and supervisors of the company adhere to the principle of integrity management, and have not yet purchased liability insurance for directors and supervisors. In the future, they will understand and evaluate the liability insurance for directors and supervisors as needed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;width:652.55pt&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:新細明體,serif&quot;&gt;八、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:STKaiti&quot;&gt;If there is a corporate governance self-assessment report or a corporate governance assessment report entrusted by other professional institutions, the results of the self-assessment (or outsourced assessment), major deficiencies (or suggestions), and improvements should be stated: None.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
	&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:start&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000&quot;&gt;Note 1: For the training situation of directors and supervisors, please refer to the regulations of the &amp;quot;Reference Example of the Implementation Points of Training for Directors and Supervisors of Listed Companies&amp;quot; issued by the Taiwan Stock Exchange Corporation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:start&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000&quot;&gt;Note 2: In the case of securities dealers, securities investment trust enterprises, securities investment consulting enterprises and futures dealers, the implementation of risk management policies, risk measurement standards, and consumer or customer protection policies shall be described.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:start&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000&quot;&gt;Note 3: The so-called corporate governance self-assessment report refers to the report on the current company operation and implementation in the respective assessment projects, which are assessed and explained by the company according to the corporate governance self-assessment project.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

company-2.html.c_text_tw:
&lt;h2&gt;經營者話&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;span style=&quot;font-family:微軟正黑體&quot;&gt;2025年6月18日正式接棒之際，我由衷感謝張雅琍董事長多年以來的奉獻與堅持，為寶得利奠定深厚而珍貴的基礎。她留下的不只是品牌，更是一份「行銷台灣」的使命與初心。未來我將承續這份精神，帶領寶得利走向下一個成長與蛻變的新篇章。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:微軟正黑體&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;這幾年來，我們共同見證了世界的變化。疫情之後的全球觀光市場尚未完全復甦，而兩岸旅遊遲未重新開放，讓陪伴台灣觀光產&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:微軟正黑體&quot;&gt;業超過十年的寶得利，也必須面對前所未見的挑戰。我常常告訴團隊：&lt;strong&gt;「市場不會為任何人停留，但我們可以選擇怎麼迎接下一個時代。」&lt;/strong&gt;正因如此，寶得利的下一步，必須比以往更加勇敢，也更加堅定。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:微軟正黑體&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;寶得利曾因觀光熱潮而蓬勃成長，是旅客眼中代表台灣美好工藝的品牌。然而環境變化讓我們明白，不能再將希望寄托於單一市場，也不能依靠過去的成功去支撐未來。所以，我們重新審視自己。我們看到『&lt;strong&gt;市場在變，顧客在變&lt;/strong&gt;』『&lt;strong&gt;產業在重組，科技在改寫商業模式&lt;/strong&gt;』『&lt;strong&gt;舊的經濟動能不會再回到過去&lt;/strong&gt;』在這樣的時代，堅守本業固然重要，但「轉型」已不只是選擇，而是責任 &amp;mdash; &amp;nbsp;對股東、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:微軟正黑體&quot;&gt;對員工、對寶得利。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:微軟正黑體&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 我深知，轉型是一條不容易的路。但我也相信，每一次環境的劇變，都是企業重生的契機。寶得利從 1970 年代走到今天，本就不是因為幸運，而是靠著堅持、踏實與不放棄。如今，我們將透過多角化經營，讓公司站穩新市場，確保寶得利的下一個十年，不僅能穩定，更能茁壯。這段期間，感謝所有股東、同仁與合作夥伴的信任。我會帶領公司不斷前行，讓寶得利從一次次的挑戰中淬鍊更強的體質，以更多元的服務、更具前瞻的策略，迎向屬於我們的新未來。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;董事長 &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 黃武琦 &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/images/upload/2025_11_30_093420.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float:right; height:241px; width:160px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

company-2.html.c_text_en:
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:start&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:medium&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:STKaiti&quot;&gt;Message from the Chairman&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;On June 18, 2025, as I officially assumed leadership, I extend my heartfelt gratitude to Chairwoman Chang Ya-Li for her years of dedication and perseverance, which laid a solid and invaluable foundation for Baodeli. She left behind more than a brand&amp;mdash;she passed on a mission and an unwavering commitment to &amp;ldquo;promoting Taiwan to the world.&amp;rdquo; I will carry forward this spirit as I lead Baodeli into its next chapter of growth and transformation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;In recent years, we have all witnessed the profound changes shaping the world. The global tourism market has yet to fully recover after the pandemic, and cross-strait travel remains suspended. For Baodeli&amp;mdash;an enterprise that has stood alongside Taiwan&amp;rsquo;s tourism industry for more than a decade&amp;mdash;this has presented unprecedented challenges. I often remind our team:&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;The market will not wait for anyone, but we can choose how we face the next era.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;For this reason, Baodeli must now move forward with greater courage and determination than ever before.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;Baodeli once flourished amid the tourism boom, becoming a beloved symbol of Taiwan&amp;rsquo;s craftsmanship for countless international visitors. Yet the changing environment taught us that we can no longer rely on a single market, nor depend on past success to sustain the future. And so, we took a hard look at ourselves.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;We clearly see that:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;The market is changing, customers are changing.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;Industries are restructuring, and technology is reshaping business models.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;The old economic drivers will not return as before.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;In such an era, safeguarding our core business is important, but&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;transformation&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;is no longer a choice&amp;mdash;it is a responsibility to our shareholders, our employees, and to Baodeli itself.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;I understand that transformation is never easy. Yet I also believe that every major shift in the environment creates an opportunity for rebirth. Baodeli has survived and evolved since the 1970s not because of luck, but because of perseverance, discipline, and an unwavering refusal to give up.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;Today, through diversified operations, we are positioning the company to stand firmly in new markets and ensuring that Baodeli&amp;rsquo;s next decade will not only be stable, but thrive. I am deeply grateful for the trust placed in us by our shareholders, colleagues, and partners. I will continue to lead Baodeli forward&amp;mdash;strengthened by every challenge we overcome&amp;mdash;and with broader services and a more forward-looking strategy, we will embrace a future that truly belongs to us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;
             &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt; Chairman                               
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Tommy Huang&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;     &lt;/span&gt;

&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/images/upload/2025_11_30_093420.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float:right; height:241px; width:160px&quot; /&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;

company-3.html.c_text_tw:
