&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:24px&quot;&gt;Corporate Social Responsibility&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fulfill social responsibilities, including the systems and measures adopted by the company for environmental protection, community participation, social contribution, social services, social welfare, consumer rights, human rights, safety and health, and other social responsibility activities and their implementation status.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width:100%; word-wrap:break-word&quot;&gt;
	&lt;tbody&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;width:35%&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;Subject&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;width:35%&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;Operational Status&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;width:30%&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;Differences and reasons with the Code of Practice for Corporate Social Responsibility of Listed OTC Companies&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;一、Implement and promote corporate governance&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;&amp;lt;
			&lt;p&gt;(一)The company formulates corporate social responsibility policies or systems, and reviews the implementation results.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(一)The company has not yet formulated a corporate social responsibility policy, but the company will continue to practice corporate social responsibility, and may formulate relevant policies in the future depending on the situation.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(一)Relevant policies will be discussed in the future.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(二) The company sets up the operation of professional (part-time) units to promote corporate social responsibility.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(二)At present, the company has not set up a full-time (part-time) unit to promote corporate social responsibility.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(二)At present, the company has not set up a full-time (part-time) unit to promote corporate social responsibility.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(三)The company regularly organizes corporate ethics education, training and publicity for directors, supervisors and employees, and combines them with the employee performance appraisal system to establish a clear and effective reward and punishment system.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(三)&amp;nbsp;The company&amp;#39;s directors and supervisors arrange continuous training every year; internally, there is an employee education and training and employee performance appraisal system, and the mutual relationship is used to promote corporate governance and employee self-discipline.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;(三)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;二、develop a sustainable environment&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(一)The company is committed to improving the utilization efficiency of various resources and using recycled materials with low impact on the environment.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(一)The company aims to be paperless, and all documents that do not need to use paper will be replaced by electronic documents to reduce the amount of paper and the felling of trees.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(一)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(二)According to its industrial characteristics, circumstances where the company has established an appropriate environmental management system.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(二)The company formulates relevant environmental policies according to its industrial characteristics, in order to pursue beautification, greening and pollution-free to ensure a safe and healthy new environment.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(二)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(三)Established special unit or personnel for environmental management to maintain the environment&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(三)The employees of the company should keep the surrounding environment clean, and send people to inspect and maintain the sanitation of the office on a regular basis.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(三)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(四)The company pays attention to the impact of climate change on operating activities, and formulates the company&amp;#39;s energy conservation and carbon reduction and greenhouse gas reduction strategies.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(四)Cooperate with the government to implement various measures of energy saving and carbon reduction, and organize energy saving and carbon saving actions for the enterprise internally or externally to fulfill the environmental protection responsibility of the enterprise in the global village. Such as: paperless, green, and low-carbon meetings, carbon emission control, air conditioning/lighting power saving and water saving, etc.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(四)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;三、Maintain social welfare&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(一)The company abides by relevant labor laws and regulations and respects the internationally recognized principles of basic labor rights, protects the legitimate rights and interests of employees and non-discriminatory treatment in employment policies, etc., and establishes appropriate management methods, procedures, and implementation conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(一)The company formulates &amp;quot;work rules&amp;quot; in accordance with labor standards laws and regulations for employees to abide by and protect their legitimate rights and interests, and formulate relevant management measures and procedures to govern the company according to them.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(一)&amp;nbsp;no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(二)The company provides employees with a safe and healthy working environment, and regularly implements safety and health education for employees.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(二)The company maintains fire-fighting equipment and conducts fire safety education and training from time to time; and regularly sends relevant personnel to check drinking water equipment and replace filter elements, so that employees can drink healthily.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(二)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(三)The company establishes a mechanism for employees to communicate regularly, and informs employees of operational changes that may have a significant impact on employees in a reasonable manner.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(三)The company adopts an open two-way communication method for the publicity of the company&amp;#39;s policies and the understanding of employees&amp;#39; opinions.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(三)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(四)The company develops and discloses its consumer rights policy and provides transparent and effective consumer grievance procedures for its products and services.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(四)The company clearly provides the after-sales service process at the time of sales; if there is any customer complaint, it will be dealt with and notified to the relevant department heads at the first time.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(四)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(五)The company cooperates with suppliers in a joint effort to improve the situation of corporate social responsibility.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(五)The company continues to introduce high-quality products that are in line with environmental protection, and establishes good relationships with suppliers to work together to fulfill social responsibilities.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(五)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(六)The company participates in community development and charitable organizations related activities through business activities, in-kind donations, corporate volunteer services or other free professional services.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(六)The company promises to fulfill its corporate social responsibility in order to realize the concept of &amp;quot;take from the society and use it for the society&amp;quot;. Participate in and sponsor various cultural and social welfare activities from time to time, and fulfill the role of corporate citizenship in addition to the pursuit of corporate growth.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(六)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;四、Strengthen information disclosure&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(一)How the company discloses relevant and reliable CSR-related information.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td rowspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;The company will gradually disclose social responsibility related information in the company&amp;#39;s annual report, public prospectus or according to the company&amp;#39;s development situation in accordance with the relevant information disclosure regulations.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(一)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(二)The company prepares a corporate social responsibility report to disclose the promotion of corporate social responsibility.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;(二)no significant difference&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;五、If the company has its own CSR code based on the &amp;quot;Practice for Corporate Social Responsibility of Listed Companies&amp;quot;, please describe the difference between its operation and the code: the company has not formulated a CSR code, so it is not applicable.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;六、Other important information that helps to understand the operation of corporate social responsibility (such as the company&amp;#39;s systems and practices for environmental protection, community participation, social contribution, social services, social welfare, consumer rights, human rights, safety and health, and other social responsibility activities) measures and implementation): none.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;七、If the company&amp;#39;s product or corporate social responsibility report has passed the verification standards of the relevant verification agencies, it should be stated: None.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
	&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

